issue.title: [CF 1212] [Beta] Cannot find "LibBabble-3.0"
issue.body:
What version of TellMeWhen are you using? v8.0.0 r85 (g5bcf9c1)

Do you have an error log of what happened?

``` 19x ...bble-CreatureType-3.0\LibBabble-CreatureType-3.0.lua:14: Cannot find a library instance of "LibBabble-3.0". [C]: in function `error' BugSack\Libs\LibStub\LibStub.lua:38: in function `LibStub' ...bble-CreatureType-3.0\LibBabble-CreatureType-3.0.lua:14: in main chunk Locals: (*temporary) = "Cannot find a library instance of "LibBabble-3.0"." ```

Please provide any additional information below. It appears that LibBabble-3.0 isn't required in the toc file.
